modName: Remove all Halos Posers spells batch
summary: This is a quick couple of batch files I came up with to remove and re-add all the spells of Halo's Poser S!
descriptionHtml: This is a quick couple of batch files I came up with to remove and re-add all the spells of Halo's Poser S V1.6 and as a bonus it removes the Aloe Poser spell. After downloading just type [i]bat rmposerspell [/i]and all of the spells will be removed! To add them back just type [i]bat addposerspell[/i]Â and they will return!
